::CyberShark::

    "Unit Megatron found, triangulating.....unable to triangulate." 
CyberShark's computer said.
    "Just give me a general location," CyberShark said.
    "Sector 000 in a 360 degree angle around unit CyberShark," The computer 
said.
    "He's below me?" CyberShark did his best to look down, he ended up doing 
a dive for a cliff. "Wha, that's not good." He pulled up just in time. He 
circled in a downward spiral towards the base of the cliff. Once there he 
transformed to Robot Mode.
    "Megatron? Are you here? I am CyberShark, we must speak," CyberShark 
said, feeling a little bit of fear since he didn't know where Megatron was, 
and hid namesake was Megatron.
